    • Method Detail

      • onEditPageLoad

        public void onEditPageLoad(com.ami.mse.ucms.db.entities.component.Component component)
        Called when edit component page is load. Initialize componentValueList as new ArrayList. Makes current component that will be edited to be component that the user is chose. If the component is of type SelectOneMenu, extracts it values from the data base and pass them to componentValuesList.
        Parameters:
        component - - the component that the user is chose in the view-components page.

      • save

        public String save()
        Saves the instance of the Component with all attributes. If the added component is a type OneSelectMenu the method creates instance new of the ComponentValue. This instance saves the values for the OneSelectMenu component. Set message for success or fail to save the component.
        Returns:
        reload create-component page.

      • edit

        public String edit()
        Used to update instance of existing Component. Checks if the name of the updated component is equals to the name of the other existing component. If it is true sets warning message. If the component that the user wants to update is of type SelectOneMenu also saves the new or edited values of this menu. Sets completeMessage if update is successful.

      • removeValue

        public void removeValue(String value)
        Used to remove values from the componentValuesList used to saves the values for the component of type SelectOneMenu. This method is called when component of this type is updated. It is called from the button in edit-component page. Checks if componentValueList isn't empty and if the value that the user want to remove is in that list.
        Parameters:
        value - -the value that the user want to remove from the list

      • dropDownMenuSelected

        public void dropDownMenuSelected()
        Called when the value is change in the OneSelectMenu for the type of the component. Change the state of the valuesFormRender to true if the selected type is OneSelectMenu. Initialize componentValuesList as new ArrayList.

      • findAllComponents

        public List<com.ami.mse.ucms.db.entities.component.Component> findAllComponents()

        Returns:
        List of Component

      • convertCompType

        public String convertCompType(int typeNum)
        Convert the integer type of the components that are save in the data base into string values. Called when view-components page is loaded. Uses ComponentTypeConstants.
        Parameters:
        typeNum - - integer representation of the component type
        Returns:
        String representation of the component type
